      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just dont see how i'm supposed to do this. he was my whole life for ten years and now i just wake up and he isn't there and it feels like the air is gone. i cant breathe. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen but nothing ever does. it's just empty. everything is just so empty and it's never gonna stop being this way.",
